      "id": "leverage_secrets",
      "text": "Use what you know",
      "description": "Information is power. Time to use it.",
      "resultText": "You start strategically deploying your knowledge—a hint here, a revelation there, carefully calibrated to advance your interests. People learn that you know things, that crossing you means their secrets might come to light. The power is real and intoxicating. But so is the isolation. Nobody trusts you anymore, and you can't blame them. You've become the kind of person who trades in secrets, and that changes how people see you. How you see yourself.",
