      "id": "keep_secrets",
      "text": "Guard what you know carefully",
      "description": "Knowledge brings responsibility.",
      "resultText": "You treat the secrets as sacred trusts, carefully protecting each confidence. When others try to get you to share what you know, you deflect. When you're tempted to use information for gain, you resist. It's exhausting—the constant vigilance, the burden of being the keeper of so many hidden truths. But people learn they can trust you with sensitive information. You become a confessor, a vault. Valued, but also lonely.",
